This dev board can be powered by AC 90V-250Vï¼ŒDC 7-12V or DC 5V via microUSB. Choose only one of the three!

Led2i is connected to GPIO15. You can unassign it or control it using "LedPower2" command.

### Flashing
***WARNING: DO NOT IN ANY CIRCUMSTANCE OPERATE THE DEVICE WHILE CONNECTED TO AC POWER***

Flash using any of the provided TX/RX headers and GND. Do not connect VCC from the USB-to-serial adapter but power the module using micro USB. 

